schools.name: Irwin & Susan Molasky Junior High School

data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom/3 bath home in great NW area.  Home is turn-key ready.  Formal living and dining areas when you enter the house with high vaulted ceilings and tons of natural light.  Kitchen is gorgeous with stainless upgraded refrigerator, breakfast bar, separate eating area and the list goes on. Home has solar panels for those energy efficient buyers (Buyer to assume).  Great Primary retreat with multiple closets and newly updated primary bath and shower.  Inground spa with rock accents and a great outdoor area.  Great solid surface flooring in walking areas including stairs.  Community is close to all.
